sbmlme.converter

Class MEJsonProcessDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • sbmlme.converter.MEJsonProcessDataType

  • public class MEJsonProcessDataType
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the different types of process data in a COBRAme JSON schema. Any process data object in a COBRAme model needs to have one and only one of the declared types in this class.
    Author:
    Marc A. Voigt

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      private MEJsonProcessDataTypeAttributes ComplexData
      The type of process data that encode information of a single complex formation reaction.
      private MEJsonProcessDataTypeAttributes GenericData
      The type of process data that encode information of all generic formation reactions that produce the same generic component.
      private MEJsonProcessDataTypeAttributes PostTranslationData
      The type of process data that encode information of a single post translation reaction.
      private MEJsonProcessDataTypeAttributes StoichiometricData
      The type of process data that encode information of up to two metabolic reactions.
